<HEADLINE>
FT  11 DEC 93 / Link road opened
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Tim Sainsbury, industry minister, yesterday opened the southern section
of a Pounds 50m spine road in Bristol. The 2km road, due for completion next
summer, links the M32 with the A4.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
