<HEADLINE>
FT  10 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Gt Portland chief sells shares
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Richard Peskin, chairman and managing director of Great Portland Estates,
sold on Tuesday 750,000 shares, representing a little more than 25 per cent
of his holding in the company. The shares were placed by Cazenove at 225p.
Mr Peskin said he had no intention of selling any further beneficial shares
within the next 18 to 24 months. He and his family still retain a holding of
more than 2.1m shares.
